dct_title_s: Fu-chou (Foochow) and Nan-t'ai, China, Fukien Province
dct_description_sm: "Compiled in 1945 from China 1:50,000 Army Map Service 8833 II (Type C) 1945. Planimetric detail intensified from aerial photography dated 1944-45 by photo-planimetric methods with reference to Fu-chou 1:10,000, General Staff (Fukien Office), 1934."
"Place names were transcribed according to the modified Wade-Giles System."
Some streets and buildings are named; wooded and cultivated areas are shown.
Marginal maps: Coverage diagram -- Index to boundaries.
